---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services – Florida Garage Pros | Garage Door Repair in Florida"
  description="Explore all garage door services offered by Florida Garage Pros — repair, spring replacement, opener repair, new installations, and emergency service across Florida."
  activePage="services"
>
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-blue-dark text-white py-16 px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-3">Our Garage Door Services</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-blue-200 max-w-xl mx-auto">Professional, fast, and affordable solutions for every garage door problem in Florida.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Services List -->
  <main class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-12">

      <!-- Service 1: Garage Door Repair -->
      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-5xl shrink-0">🔧</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Garage Door Repair</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Whether your garage door is making strange noises, moving unevenly, or won't open at all — our technicians can diagnose and fix the problem fast. We repair broken panels, damaged tracks, frayed cables, worn rollers, and more.
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Broken panels &amp; sections</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Off-track doors</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Damaged cables &amp; pulleys</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Worn rollers &amp; hinges</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Weather seal replacement</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Noisy door lubrication &amp; tune-up</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="inline-block bg-brand-orange hover:bg-brand-orange-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors">
            📞 Call for Repair
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Service 2: Spring Replacement -->
      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-5xl shrink-0">🔩</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Spring Replacement</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            A broken garage door spring is the most common reason a door stops working. Springs are under extreme tension — attempting a DIY fix is dangerous. Our certified technicians safely replace both torsion and extension springs, restoring your door to full operation.
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Torsion spring replacement</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Extension spring replacement</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> High-cycle spring upgrades</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Spring tension adjustment</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Same-day service available</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Safety cable installation</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="inline-block bg-brand-orange hover:bg-brand-orange-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors">
            📞 Call for Spring Replacement
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Service 3: Opener Repair -->
      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-5xl shrink-0">⚙️</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Opener Repair &amp; Replacement</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Is your garage door opener unresponsive, slow, or acting erratically? We service and replace all major brands of garage door openers, including smart openers with Wi-Fi connectivity. Get your opener working like new or upgrade to a modern model.
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> LiftMaster service &amp; repair</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Chamberlain &amp; Genie service</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Remote &amp; keypad programming</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Smart Wi-Fi opener installation</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Safety sensor alignment</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Drive belt/chain/screw repair</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="inline-block bg-brand-orange hover:bg-brand-orange-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors">
            📞 Call for Opener Service
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Service 4: New Installations -->
      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-5xl shrink-0">🚪</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">New Door Installations</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Ready for a new garage door? We carry a wide selection of residential and commercial doors in various styles, materials, and finishes. Our team handles complete installation — from removing the old door to full hardware setup and testing.
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Residential door installation</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Commercial door installation</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Steel, wood &amp; aluminum doors</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Insulated door options</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Custom size doors</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Old door removal included</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="inline-block bg-brand-orange hover:bg-brand-orange-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors">
            📞 Call for Installation Quote
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Service 5: Emergency Service -->
      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-blue-50 border border-brand-blue rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-5xl shrink-0">🚨</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Emergency Garage Door Service</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Stuck inside your garage? Door won't close at night? Security is compromised? We offer emergency garage door service 7 days a week. Our technicians are dispatched quickly to get your door functional and your home secure.
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Available 7 days a week</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Fast dispatch — 1–2 hour arrival</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Stuck or jammed doors</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Door won't close (security fix)</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Broken springs (urgent)</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-orange font-bold">✔</span> Vehicle trapped inside</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="inline-block bg-brand-blue hover:bg-brand-blue-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors">
            📞 Emergency: (555) 123-4567
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="bg-brand-orange py-12 px-4 text-center text-white">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">Ready to Get Your Garage Door Fixed?</h2>
    <p class="text-orange-100 mb-6 text-lg">Call us now for a free estimate — same-day service available.</p>
    <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="inline-block bg-white text-brand-orange hover:bg-orange-50 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-xl transition-colors shadow-lg">
      📞 Call (555) 123-4567
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
